column7: Exercise 8: Please note, you can use any method to find the answer.
Draw some key analysis in this dataset
Find the top three highest performing students for Maths
Find the top three highest performing students for English
Find the top three highest performing students for Science
Find the student(s) with the highest variance (range) of scores
With the information above, write a few lines on the overall analysis of the dataset (3 to 5 lines)
* Ben exceeded expectations in Maths, sharing the top mark with Lisa, as he was below average in English and had poor results in Science
* Although Lisa had the top mark in English, Funke also excelled as had the 2nd highest score despite being very poor in Maths and average in Science
* Ciara exceeded expectations in Science as achieved the top mark yet did very poor in English and was below average in Maths
* Lisa is the most consistent student in her scores across all 3 subjects
